  <div xmlns:v="http://rdf.data-vocabulary.org/#" typeof="v:Review">
    <div class="main review-item" id="4574198">
        

  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/4574198/" class="title-link">不会让我觉得特别枯燥的书</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-4574198"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/48408232/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u48408232-1.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/48408232/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">joooooody</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar40 main-title-rating" title="推荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2011-01-11"
      class="main-meta">2011-01-11 10:29:29</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_4574198_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  最大的有点是小而轻，很方便携带，在等车的空隙，乘车的途中都可以随手读来。一般此类书籍应该比较枯燥乏味，虽然此书乍一看也如此，但是读起来会感觉时间过的很快，在回家的地铁上，不自觉的就到了终点站。但是读一遍应该不会全部理解，需要多读几遍。

                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">0有用 / 0没用</span>
